### Registrar Farmacêutico
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/registro
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "José Carlos",
    "email": "jose@email.com",
    "senha": "jose123",
    "role": "farmaceutico"
}

### Registrar Comprador 1
